file.name: complex_xml.yaml
file.content:
---
openapi: "3.0.2"
info:
  title: "Complex XML"
  version: "1.0"
servers:
- url: "http://example.com/api"
paths:
  /complex/{pathParam}:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/xml:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Complex"
        required: true
      parameters:
      - name: "pathParam"
        schema:
          type: "string"
        in: "path"
        required: true
      - name: "queryParam"
        schema:
          type: "integer"
        in: "query"
        required: false
      responses:
        default:
          description: "OK"
      operationId: "complexOperation"
components:
  schemas:
    Complex:
      type: "object"
      properties:
        id:
          minimum: 0
          type: "integer"
          xml:
            attribute: true
        date:
          format: "date-time"
          type: "string"
          xml:
            name: "date-time"
        status:
          default: "value2"
          enum:
          - "value1"
          - "value2"
          - "value3"
          type: "string"
        children:
          type: "array"
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/Child"
          xml:
            wrapped: true
        complete:
          default: false
          type: "boolean"
      xml:
        name: "complex"
        namespace: "http://example.com/Complex"
    Child:
      type: "object"
      properties:
        name:
          minLength: 1
          type: "string"
          xml:
            attribute: true
        description:
          type: "string"
      xml:
        name: "child"
        namespace: "http://example.com/Child"

Error: notImplemented: path "/complex/{pathParam}": post: requestBody: contents: unsupported content types: [application/xml]
